creator: Twisto.cz
descriptionHtml:
Twisto is a modern payment application that makes your life easier. Use it to make payments online, in stores, or even to pay invoices and postal orders. It’s quick, safe, and convenient.

Registration is a breeze
Open a Twisto account and take advantage of all that Twisto offers. Download the app and finish your registration in just a couple of minutes.

Spending under control
See a quick summary of all of your purchases in one place. It even shows you the total amount you’ve spent as well as how much you still have available on your account. We also send you a daily spending summary along after each purchase so you can always stay on top of your finances.

A secure way to pay
Twisto operates as a licensed payment institution with a track record going back several years. Your Twisto account won’t be connected to your personal banking account in any way.

The best exchange rates
Take advantage of foreign exchange rates that you just can’t get anywhere else. So whether you’re going on holiday, or just surfing the web from your living room, Twisto makes all of your adventures a little sweeter.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Virtual card is now active automatically right after registration. Once your account is approved, you're ready to shop immediately.

title: Twisto – Pay your way

creator: Twisto.cz
descriptionHtml:
Twisto is a modern payment application that makes your life easier. Use it to make payments online, in stores, or even to pay invoices and postal orders. It’s quick, safe, and convenient.

Registration is a breeze
Open a Twisto account and take advantage of all that Twisto offers. Download the app and finish your registration in just a couple of minutes.

Spending under control
See a quick summary of all of your purchases in one place. It even shows you the total amount you’ve spent as well as how much you still have available on your account. We also send you a daily spending summary along after each purchase so you can always stay on top of your finances.

A secure way to pay
Twisto operates as a licensed payment institution with a track record going back several years. Your Twisto account won’t be connected to your personal banking account in any way.

The best exchange rates
Take advantage of foreign exchange rates that you just can’t get anywhere else. So whether you’re going on holiday, or just surfing the web from your living room, Twisto makes all of your adventures a little sweeter.
